        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2021-07-15 15:47:50.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(1 comment)\n\nHi Abdel,\nin OOM we have the ability to give a truststore with all needed CA (ONAP one, several privates one, public ones, ...)\nWe could think use the previous behavior is TRUSTSTORE_FILE env file is not given and use the truststore given by TRUSTSTORE_FILE (along with TRUSTSTORE_PASSWD) if present.\n\nWhat do you think?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "7325de7cc7f3da04e192481e3e88720749362e4d",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 87,
